title: Smart Mexican-Inspired Beef Patties with Tomato, Charred Corn and Spinach Salad
description: Shake up dinnertime with a loaded, smart salad of savoury, Mexican-spiced beef patties, spinach, tomatoes, charred corn and, of course, tangy ranch to tie it all together!

